---
// Composant About pour la section "À propos"
---

<div class="about-us-section py-20" id="aboutus">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="row flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <!-- About Left Image Start -->
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="row flex flex-col sm:flex-row">
            <div class="col-7 w-full sm:w-7/12">
              <div class="about-img right-shape">
                <figure class="reveal hover-anime">
                  <img
                    src="/images/about-img-1.jpg"
                    alt=""
                    class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
                  />
                </figure>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-5 w-full sm:w-5/12">
              <div class="about-year-image">
                <div
                  class="bg-[#222222] text-white text-center text-3xl px-8 py-6 rounded-tl-full rounded-tr-full rounded-bl-full mb-4 w-full"
                >
                  <p>Depuis</p>
                  <h4 class="counter font-bold">1998</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="about-img left-shape">
                  <figure class="reveal hover-anime">
                    <img
                      src="/images/about-img-2.jpg"
                      alt=""
                      class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
                    />
                  </figure>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- About Left Image End -->
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6 w-full lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12 mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <!-- Section Title Start -->
        <div class="section-title">
          <h3
            class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4 animate-fade-in-up"
          >
            À propos de NEAT
          </h3>
          <h2
            class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up"
          >
            Le salon de coiffure qui vous fera vous sentir unique
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- Section Title End -->

        <!-- About Content Start -->
        <div class="about-content animate-fade-in-left">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Lorem Ipsum est simplement un texte factice de l'industrie de
            l'impression et de la composition. Lorem Ipsum est le texte factice
            standard de l'industrie.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 flex-shrink-0">01.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"
                >La coupe et le coiffage avec 10 ans d'expérience.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 flex-shrink-0">02.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"
                >Mise à jour des dernières technologies et tendances dans le
                monde.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 flex-shrink-0">03.</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600"
                >Utilisation des meilleurs produits des fournisseurs de premier
                plan.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="#"
            class="btn-default inline-block px-8 py-3 border-2 border-gray-900 text-gray-900 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 font-medium"
            >Lire plus</a
          >
        </div>
        <!-- About Content End -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
